pageContext.claim: “She's got a certain talent [Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez], but you know, all of a sudden she had no money, nothing, and all of a sudden she had $2 million. And she spent the $2 million all over the place, her and a boyfriend. … If a Republican did that, they'd be in jail. … Dresses, rent, other things.”
pageContext.analysis: Ocasio-Cortez did not spend $2 million on her boyfriend, dresses and rent, though she did raise questions about potential self-dealing through an aide's use of a PAC that funneled hundreds of thousands of dollars to an affiliated LLC and her boyfriend.
